'''巴罕'''（{{lang-so|Badhan}}; {{lang-ar|برن}}）名義上是[[索馬利亞|索馬利亞]]的都市，位在該國東北部，目前由[[邦特蘭|邦特蘭]]實質統治。<ref>{{cite web |title=Somalia’s Puntland Army Takes Over Badhan to Block Somaliland Parliamentary, Municipal Elections |url=https://www.somtribune.com/2021/01/25/somalias-puntland-army-takes-over-badhan-to-block-somaliland-parliamentary-municipal-elections/ |website=Somtribune |publisher=Puntland Post |access-date=2021-06-07 |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429185441/https://www.somtribune.com/2021/01/25/somalias-puntland-army-takes-over-badhan-to-block-somaliland-parliamentary-municipal-elections/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>人口31,655（2014年）。<ref name="Somalia Population Survey">{{Cite web |url=https://somalia.unfpa.org/sites/default/files/pub-pdf/Population-Estimation-Survey-of-Somalia-PESS-2013-2014.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-11 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902035331/https://somalia.unfpa.org/sites/default/files/pub-pdf/Population-Estimation-Survey-of-Somalia-PESS-2013-2014.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
