== 概述 ==
雨季时常有洪水泛滥的危险。 1971 年，<ref>{{Cite web|title=ENVIRONMENTAL STUDY OF DEGRADATION IN THE SOOL PLATEAU AND GEBI VALLEY: SANAAG REGION OF NORTHERN SOMALIA|url=https://www.faoswalim.org/resources/Land/Environmental_Study_Degradation_Sool_Plateau_and_Gebi.pdf|access-date=2006-02-02|author=Simon Mumuli Oduori|archive-date=2019-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819060736/http://www.faoswalim.org/resources/Land/Environmental_Study_Degradation_Sool_Plateau_and_Gebi.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该镇被重新安置在一个名为 Badhan 的钻孔附近，从那时起它就一直沿用这个名字。该地区最初是在 14 世纪由 Darod 氏族 Warsangali 亚氏族的索马里牧民定居的，因为那里有水供他们的羊群使用。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/Deportation_letter_of_Sultan_Mohamoud_Ali_Shire%2C_Ex-Sultan_of_Warsangeli.jpg/368px-Deportation_letter_of_Sultan_Mohamoud_Ali_Shire%2C_Ex-Sultan_of_Warsangeli.jpg |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-09-10 |archive-date=2021-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210614161951/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/Deportation_letter_of_Sultan_Mohamoud_Ali_Shire,_Ex-Sultan_of_Warsangeli.jpg/368px-Deportation_letter_of_Sultan_Mohamoud_Ali_Shire,_Ex-Sultan_of_Warsangeli.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref> 


巴丹也因穆罕默德·阿卜杜拉·哈桑的托钵僧与瓦尔桑杰利苏丹国之间的战斗而闻名。苦行僧的领袖哈桑下令在该市建造一座新的大堡垒。 <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://wardheernews.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/An-appraisal-of-the-%E2%80%98Dervish-state%E2%80%99_Marcus.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-09-10 |archive-date=2021-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608213733/https://wardheernews.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/An-appraisal-of-the-%E2%80%98Dervish-state%E2%80%99_Marcus.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>如今，堡垒需要修复，因为时间已经磨损了它。

